返孝子算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ca4f92f69bb965bc46fd6bb6c0dd3d04b76023","tid":282163,"uid":3164,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:34:12.000Z","msg":"放低佢係酒店瞓個晏覺你先鼠出去啦仆街仔<br />\n你老母人生路不熟<br />\n一陣佢以為你賣甩佢佢就騰曬雞咁好撚慘㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a916735faeb0535bd356c5a939ca8e08a9669eec","tid":282163,"uid":61902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:36:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>東京送佢地上晴空塔，一係就雷門<br />\n再唔係就動物園水旅館<br />\n<br />\n我去大阪呀<br />\n有咩地方放低呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌我都係同老母去大阪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同問</blockquote><br />\n放你老母起心齋橋個頭大把嘢行</blockquote><br />\n咁我直頭book個頭酒店，佢地行完自己返酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚驚佢地蕩失路，但我又好想去買av<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買多兩張電話卡比佢地好似安全d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n實蕩失路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係想嚇你<br />\n同得你去旅行基本上都旨意晒你，根本唔會認路<br />\n跟住你行就係架啦，你突然叫佢地自己行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老母老唔老先，如果識用google map都好D<br />\n唔識嘅話你近近地搵間coffee shop叫佢等陣吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前去台灣，都試過佢兩個晨早流流落街<br />\n由台北車站行去西門町再返酒店既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3df5275a379097be59599ad482a66f1e7717037","tid":282163,"uid":13199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:37:56.000Z","msg":"搵個商場，有超市又有&yen;100店（大型店）俾佢慢慢行。一定要俾上網咭佢同教佢whatsapp call。<br />\n叫佢點行都唔可以離開個商場。<br />\n頂多三四個鐘好喇，太耐驚佢冇嘢行/肚餓行咗出去搵嘢食/佢冇安全感。"},{"pid":"574e7e686004e465603fe134ae1c13650f477c76","tid":282163,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:38:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>東京送佢地上晴空塔，一係就雷門<br />\n再唔係就動物園水旅館<br />\n<br />\n我去大阪呀<br />\n有咩地方放低呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌我都係同老母去大阪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同問</blockquote><br />\n放你老母起心齋橋個頭大把嘢行</blockquote><br />\n咁我直頭book個頭酒店，佢地行完自己返酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚驚佢地蕩失路，但我又好想去買av<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買多兩張電話卡比佢地好似安全d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n實蕩失路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係想嚇你<br />\n同得你去旅行基本上都旨意晒你，根本唔會認路<br />\n跟住你行就係架啦，你突然叫佢地自己行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老母老唔老先，如果識用google map都好D<br />\n唔識嘅話你近近地搵間coffee shop叫佢等陣吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前去台灣，都試過佢兩個晨早流流落街<br />\n由台北車站行去西門町再返酒店既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3aa0038846f111d8f60509c890433998e701ad6","tid":282163,"uid":61902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:38:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老母識唔識英文或日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係咩都唔得先頭痕<br />\n<br />\n佢自己一個行又擔心 我又驚佢唔識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英文日文唔洗講一定唔識<br />\n最慘係連蝗語都唔識<br />\n蕩失路搵支那大使館都搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當日都想擺老母向skytree<br />\n之後比埋wiftegg佢自己行<br />\n但佢一條友行，想問下人野又唔識，想買野問人有冇新嘅又唔識<br />\n所以你地都係放棄啦，做返孝子算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後點搵返你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e702fedc37fbe7ac30fcb7d546150d191b7b547","tid":282163,"uid":72306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:43:44.000Z","msg":"牛郎店"},{"pid":"e5ce829a980404520536bfc3775098a838c12317","tid":282163,"uid":55847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:44:37.000Z","msg":"放佢係風俗店啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729f37298ff1b75e911972e95ea77cbde3dc408a","tid":282163,"uid":39536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:46:17.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefbd8f5f98e8e87bf8b39e41f22891ce61a5db9","tid":282163,"uid":70943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:46:25.000Z","msg":"早